# Cursor — PR & CI

Authoritative source: [docs/ai/pr-and-ci.md](mdc:docs/ai/pr-and-ci.md).

Read it before opening a PR. It covers the CI-enforced title regex, the
required body sections, the local quality gates, the CI job catalog, and
the force-push policy. Title regex lives in
[`.github/workflows/pr-checks.yml`](mdc:.github/workflows/pr-checks.yml);
body template is [`.github/pull_request_template.md`](mdc:.github/pull_request_template.md).
